    "description": "Wellnet Corporation develops payment settlement, electronic billing, electronic payment, and mobile authentication services in Japan. The company provides membership management services; multipayment and money transfer services; Shimaeru, a service for concerns about electronic invoices and the electronic bookkeeping act; and Payment Secretary, a smartphone app for making payments directly from bank account. In addition, it offers Bus Mori!, an app to purchase tickets and coupons; Bus Mori! MONTA, a real-time seat reservation management system for bus operators; Bus Mori! Web Ticket Collection Site, a website for receiving bus tickets; and Altair Triple Star Cloud, a MaaS-type sales core system. Wellnet Corporation was incorporated in 1983 and is headquartered in Sapporo, Japan."
